  "name": "Draft Purchase Orders - Create a Purchase Order",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"draft-purchase-orders-create-a-purchase-order\">Draft Purchase Orders - Create a Purchase Order</h1>\n<p>To be updated on the PO article:</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Create-a-Purchase-Order\">https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Create-a-Purchase-Order</a> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>To create a Purchase Order manually:</p>\n<ol><li>Navigate to Inventory &gt; PO Management &gt; Create PO<br/><strong>Tip: </strong>You can also create a PO from the PO Manager by clicking \"Create New PO\"</li><li>Select <strong>Create a PO Manually</strong></li><li>Click <strong>New PO</strong></li><li>The <strong>Create Purchase Order </strong>window will load<br/><img alt=\"mceclip0.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807775/mceclip0.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Select the <strong>Outlet</strong></li><li>Select a <strong>Supplier</strong></li><li>Enter a <strong>Supplier Invoice Number </strong>(optional)</li><li>Click <strong>Create</strong> (bottom left-hand corner)</li><li>The <strong>Add Products </strong>tab will be displayed<br/><img alt=\"mceclip1 (32).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmbEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Either scan or manually type your <strong>product code</strong> into the blank field and click <strong>Add Item</strong><br/><div><strong>Tip: </strong>You can enter a Supplier SKU, Manufacturer SKU or Product ID</div><br/></li><li>Click the <strong>Product Search </strong>button to perform an <strong>advanced search</strong> for your required product</li><li>Click the blank <strong>Search </strong>field and either scan or manually type your product code<br/><div><strong>Tip: </strong>You can enter a Supplier SKU, Manufacturer SKU or Product ID</div><br/></li><li>Click <strong>Product Search </strong>to perform an advanced search for your required product</li><li>Once the product has been selected the <strong>Add Item to PO </strong>window will be displayed<br/><img alt=\"mceclip1.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892016/mceclip1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>If the code you have entered matches multiple products, all products will be displayed in the window (you will be able to add multiple items at once by updating the Quantity). To add only a specific product, use the drop-down box in the top right-hand corner to select the product<br/><img alt=\"mceclip2.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005892036/mceclip2.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Enter a <strong>Quantity </strong>(the number of units to be ordered)</li><li>Enter the <strong>Supplier Buy </strong>if the buy price for the product has been changed<br/><div><strong>Tip: </strong>The Supplier Buy price is the product price in the Supplier's currency - for more information refer to the article \"<a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://galaxy.maropost.com/s/article/Understanding-Supplier-Buy-and-Average-Weighted-Buy-Price\">What is the difference between Supplier Buy and Buy Price Ex</a>\")</div><br/></li><li>Click <strong>Confirm</strong><span> </span>to add the product to the Order<br/><img alt=\"addedproducttopo.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmgEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Repeat the steps for additional products to be ordered</li><li>To update the details of the Purchase Order click the <strong>Edit PO </strong>tab<br/><img alt=\"mceclip3.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005807815/mceclip3.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Click the <strong>Consolidate Items </strong>tab to add items from outstanding Incomplete Purchase Orders</li><li>A list of products will be displayed; tick the <strong>check box</strong><span> </span>at the end of the column to select the items<br/><div><strong>Tip: </strong>Click the tick box in the header row to select all products</div><br/><img alt=\"mceclip3 (19).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmlEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img><br/><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://galaxy.maropost.com/home/leaving?allowTrusted=1&amp;target=https%3A%2F%2Fress.zendesk.com%2Fhc%2Farticle_attachments%2F360004418215%2Fmceclip3.png\">Click to view full size</a></li><li>Click <strong>Move to current PO</strong></li><li>To save the Purchase Order without ordering the stock click <strong>Update</strong></li><li>To place the stock on order click <strong>Place On-Order</strong><br/><div><strong>Tip: </strong>When the stock is placed On-Order the inventory levels will be updated to reflect that an order has been made for these products. Purchase Orders cannot be received without the order first being marked as On-Order.</div><br/></li><li>Click <strong>Email/Preview PO </strong>to email the Purchase Order to your Supplier<br/><img alt=\"printandemail.png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmqEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Click <strong>Print </strong>to print a physical copy of the Purchase Order</li></ol><h2 data-id=\"n-a\"> </h2>\n<h2 data-id=\"quick-create-products\">Quick Create Products</h2>\n<p><strong>Create Product</strong></p>\n<p>Using this feature you can create individual products to be added to the Purchase Order</p>\n<p><img alt=\"mceclip12 (1).png\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/image.05T5g00000powmvEAA.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<ol><li>Click <strong>Create Product</strong> </li><li>Enter the new product information, including the <strong>Order Quantity</strong><br/><strong>Tip: </strong>Mandatory fields are highlighted with a red border and an asterisk</li><li>Click <strong>Create and Add</strong></li><li>The product will be simultaneously added to the Purchase Order as well as created in your database</li></ol><p> </p>\n<p><strong>Create Styles</strong></p>\n<p>This feature allows you to create products of the same style (referred to as a \"Matrix Product\") but with unique size and colour combinations (referred to as Variants).</p>\n<p>During this process a unique Supplier SKU will be automatically created for each product using the Manufacturer SKU, however this can be manually adjusted before the product is created if required.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"mceclip3.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005812795/mceclip3.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></p>\n<ol><li>Click <strong>Create Style</strong></li><li>Enter a <strong>Short Description </strong>(the name of the products)</li><li>Select a <strong>Variant Description Pattern</strong><br/><strong>Note -</strong> The Variant Description Pattern allows you to automatically create descriptions for your products to include size and/or colour attributes, or just the Short Description only</li><li>Enter the <strong>Manufacturer SKU </strong>(Style Code) used to group the products together</li><li>Select the Product Type, Brand and Season for the products</li><li>Enter the Price for the variants (this can be manually adjusted in the next step if required)</li><li>Select the Sizes and Colours for the products to be ordered</li><li>Click <strong>Configure Variants</strong></li><li>The products to be created will be displayed<br/><img alt=\"mceclip1.png\" src=\"https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png 2000w, https://ress.zendesk.com/hc/article_attachments/360005897616/mceclip1.png\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Edit the Supplier SKU, Short Description or Price fields if required</li><li>Enter a <strong>Quantity </strong>to be added to the Purchase Order</li><li>Click <strong>Create and Add</strong></li></ol><p> </p>",
